Taurus TCP 380; latest model 'c' serial #;brand new;
 never fired;box; lock; 3 mags and papers.Great little 
pocket pistol.Sell or trade for best 9 offered.

An incredible shooter!
This is it, the BIG .50 Beowulf upper.  Put it on your AR-15 lower and every hog is at risk!
Built on a DPMS Hi-Riser upper chassis with a 16 inch Saterm cut-rifling barrel  with a matching bolt and  muzzle brake for superb accuracy with the bolt riding in a DPMS BCG;
Has a Yankee Hill 9 inch hand guard over a Troy low-profile gas block;
This is all topped out with a UTG 5-MOA Red / Green dot sight.
It is a complete Beowulf package ready to hunt and will include about 70-80 rounds of Alexander 335gr.
